---
description: Recall project memory from Mnemosyne before answering questions about past decisions
alwaysApply: false
---

When the user references past work, decisions, or conversations, query the
Mnemosyne palace before answering: `mnemosyne search "<question>"` (scope
with --wing for this project). At the start of long sessions, prime context
with `mnemosyne wake-up`. Store the user's exact words with
`mnemosyne remember` when asked to remember something — never paraphrase.
